rows.label: tlk42200111_01_msg0001
rows.name: Do you know what Twinklejuice is, mo?

rows.label: tlk42200111_01_msg0003
rows.name:
When Talulu eats his favorite food,
it feels like he has more power than usual, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200111_01_msg0004
rows.name:
When you go on an adventure, you should take
lots of your favorite things with you, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200111_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But if you drink too much,
you'll get cavities and Mom will get mad,
so be careful, mo.
